The updates to Speechie v0.1.5 are as follows: Now supports Apple Watch so you can experience speech to text on your wrist. Fixed scrolling bug. Added history record function. Added support for Finnish and Russian. We have put a lot of effort into the development of this new version. If you like our new version please don t forget to give it a five star rating!
